    </blockquote>
  <br />
      <p>And finally, a pair of special pigments. <span style='color: #b0b'>Soulglimmer Pigment</span> shines with colors wholly unique to me, and <span style='color: #b0b'>Vacant Pigment</span> restores my original purplish-orange spread.</p><p><i>And all the colors I am inside have not been invented yet.</i></p>
