    </details>
        <p>Like <a href='#patterns/basics@hexcasting:raycast'><span style='color: #fc77be'>Archer&#39;s Distillation</span></a>, but instead returns the <i>entity</i> I am looking at. Costs a negligible amount of <span style='color: #74b3f2'>media</span>.</p>
    </div>
  <br />
    <div id="patterns/basics@hexcasting:print">
