          data-string="wawqwqwqwqwqw"
          data-start="east"
          data-per-world="False"
        >Your browser does not support visualizing patterns. Pattern code: wawqwqwqwqwqw</canvas>
    </details>
        <p>Like <a href='#patterns/readwrite@hexcasting:read'><span style='color: #fc77be'>Scribe&#39;s Reflection</span></a>, but the iota is read out of an entity instead of my other hand.</p>
    </div>
  <br />
    <div id="patterns/readwrite@hexcasting:write/entity">
  <h4 class="pattern-title">Chronicler&#39;s Gambit (entity, any →)<a
      href="#patterns/readwrite@hexcasting:write/entity"
      class="permalink small"
      title="Permalink"
    ><i class="bi bi-link-45deg"></i></a></h4>
    <details class="spell-collapsible">
      <summary class="collapse-spell"></summary>
        <canvas
