  <br />
      <p>A power of 3 is about as much as a Creeper&#39;s blast; 4 is about as much as a TNT blast. Nature refuses to give me a blast of more than 10 power, though.</p><p>Strangely, this explosion doesn&#39;t seem to harm me. Perhaps it&#39;s because <i>I</i> am the one exploding?</p><p>Costs a negligible amount at power 0, plus 3 extra <a href='#items/amethyst'><span style='color: #b0b'>Amethyst Dust</span></a> per point of explosion power.</p>
  <br />
