      <p>Using them is identical to using <span style='color: #b0b'>Elytra</span>; the target (which must be a player) is lofted into the air, after which pressing Space will deploy the wings. The wings are fragile, and break upon touching any surface. Longer flights may benefit from <a href='#patterns/spells/basic@hexcasting:add_motion'><span style='color: #fc77be'>Impulse</span></a> or (for the foolhardy) <span style='color: #b0b'>Fireworks</span>.</p><p>Costs about one <a href='#items/amethyst'><span style='color: #b0b'>Charged Crystal</span></a>.</p>
