        <p>Removes the top iota from the stack, and saves it to my <a href='#patterns/readwrite@hexcasting:local'><span style='color: #8d6acc'>ravenmind</span></a>, storing it there until I stop casting the <span style='color: #b38ef3'>Hex</span>.</p>
    </div>
  <br />
    <div id="patterns/readwrite@hexcasting:read/local">
