  <br />
      <p>There appear to be 16 different <span style='color: #8d6acc'>instruments</span> and 25 different <span style='color: #8d6acc'>notes</span>. Both are indexed by zero.</p><p>These seem to be the same instruments I can produce with a <span style='color: #b0b'>Note Block</span>, though the reason for each instrument&#39;s number being what it is eludes me.</p><p>Either way, I can find the numbers I need to use by inspecting a <span style='color: #b0b'>Note Block</span> through a <a href='#items/lens'><span style='color: #b0b'>Scrying Lens</span></a>.</p>
