    </details>
        <p>Costs about one <a href='#items/amethyst'><span style='color: #b0b'>Charged Amethyst</span></a>.</p>
    </div>
  <br />
    <div id="patterns/spells/hexcasting@hexcasting:craft/trinket">
  <h4 class="pattern-title">Craft Trinket (entity, [pattern] →)<a
