    </details>
        <p>Summons my <a href='#patterns/spells/sentinels'><span style='color: #8d6acc'>sentinel</span></a> at the given position. Costs about one <a href='#items/amethyst'><span style='color: #b0b'>Amethyst Dust</span></a>.</p>
    </div>
  <br />
    <div id="patterns/spells/sentinels@hexcasting:sentinel/destroy">
