        <p>Banish my <a href='#patterns/spells/sentinels'><span style='color: #8d6acc'>sentinel</span></a>, and remove it from the world. Costs a negligible amount of <span style='color: #74b3f2'>media</span>.</p>
    </div>
  <br />
    <div id="patterns/spells/sentinels@hexcasting:sentinel/get_pos">
