            <p>Like <a href='#patterns/readwrite@hexcasting:read'><span style='color: #fc77be'>Scribe&#39;s Gambit</span></a>, but the iota is written to an entity instead of my other hand.</p><p>Interestingly enough, it looks like I cannot write my own Name using this spell. I get a sense that I might be endangered if I could.</p>
        </div>
      <br />
        <div id="patterns/readwrite@hexcasting:readable">
      <h4 class="pattern-title">Auditor&#39;s Reflection (→ bool)<a
          href="#patterns/readwrite@hexcasting:readable"
