            <p>If I could save an iota into the item in my other hand, returns True. Otherwise, returns False.</p>
        </div>
      <br />
        <div id="patterns/readwrite@hexcasting:writable/entity">
      <h4 class="pattern-title">Assessor&#39;s Purification (entity → bool)<a
          href="#patterns/readwrite@hexcasting:writable/entity"
