        </details>
            <p>Remove an entity and direction from the stack, then give a shove to the given entity in the given direction. The strength of the impulse is determined by the length of the vector.<br />Costs units of <a href='#items/amethyst'><span style='color: #b0b'>Amethyst Dust</span></a> equal to the square of the length of the vector, plus one for every Impulse except the first targeting an entity.</p>
        </div>
      <br />
        <div id="patterns/spells/basic@hexcasting:blink">
      <h4 class="pattern-title">Blink (entity, number →)<a
          href="#patterns/spells/basic@hexcasting:blink"
          class="permalink small"
          title="Permalink"
        ><i class="bi bi-link-45deg"></i></a></h4>
