            <p>Add the position of my <a href='#patterns/spells/sentinels'><span style='color: #8d6acc'>sentinel</span></a> to the stack, or <a href='#casting/influences'><span style='color: #8d6acc'>Null</span></a> if it isn&#39;t summoned. Costs a negligible amount of <span style='color: #74b3f2'>media</span>.</p>
        </div>
      <br />
        <div id="patterns/spells/sentinels@hexcasting:sentinel/wayfind">
      <h4 class="pattern-title">Wayfind Sentinel (vector → vector)<a
